      "content": "got it. so it's all about heat and drying it out. i was also reading about how people sometimes call these chemical changes \"culinary magic\" or something like that because the flavor changes so much so fast. is there any way to describe the process of all those different flavor compounds forming as something more than just a series of chemical steps? like how does that complexity actually happen?",
